template.name: Docusign Document Signing
template.desc: v1.3 simple flow with single assignee. select docs via apidoc (tim's creds), fire up docusign for each document.

forms.name: Submit or Cancel
apidoc select & preview
apidoc preview
DocuSign Default Fact View

flow.name: document sign
flow.BPMNXML:
<definitions targetNamespace="http://www.activiti.org/test" expressionLanguage="http://www.w3.org/1999/XPath" typeLanguage="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:omgdi="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DI" xmlns:omgdc="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DC" xmlns:bpmndi="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/DI" xmlns:activiti="http://activiti.org/bpmn" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/MODEL">
    <message name="injectListJSON" id="injectListJSON"/>
    <process isExecutable="true" name="document sign" id="document_sign">
        <startEvent name="document sign" id="start"/>
        <sequenceFlow targetRef="serviceTask1" sourceRef="start" id="flow8"/>
        <serviceTask activiti:class="plugins.facts" name="select document" id="serviceTask1">
            <extensionElements>
                <activiti:field name="PluginKey">
                    <activiti:string>poi_selectdocument_fact</activiti:string>
                </activiti:field>
                <activiti:field name="parameterMap">
                    <activiti:expression>${getMap}</activiti:expression>
                </activiti:field>
            </extensionElements>
        </serviceTask>
        <sequenceFlow targetRef="userTask2" sourceRef="serviceTask1" id="flow9"/>
        <userTask activiti:assignee="${wf_currentAssignee}" activiti:formKey="poi_enter_form" name="enter" id="userTask2"/>
        <boundaryEvent attachedToRef="userTask2" cancelActivity="false" name="Message" id="boundarymessage10">
            <messageEventDefinition messageRef="injectListJSON"/>
        </boundaryEvent>
        <sequenceFlow targetRef="serviceTask3" sourceRef="userTask2" id="flow11"/>
        <serviceTask activiti:class="plugins.facts" name="invoke docusign" id="serviceTask3">
            <extensionElements>
                <activiti:field name="PluginKey">
                    <activiti:string>poi_invokedocusign_fact</activiti:string>
                </activiti:field>
                <activiti:field name="parameterMap">
                    <activiti:expression>${get2Map}</activiti:expression>
                </activiti:field>
            </extensionElements>
        </serviceTask>
        <sequenceFlow targetRef="userTask4" sourceRef="serviceTask3" id="flow12"/>
        <userTask activiti:assignee="${wf_currentAssignee}" activiti:formKey="poi_signorreject_form" name="sign or reject" id="userTask4"/>
        <boundaryEvent attachedToRef="userTask4" cancelActivity="false" name="Message" id="boundarymessage13">
            <messageEventDefinition messageRef="injectListJSON"/>
        </boundaryEvent>
        <sequenceFlow targetRef="end" sourceRef="userTask4" id="flow14"/>
        <endEvent name="end" id="end"/>
    </process>
</definitions>

        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="objKey">

        </activiti:field>
      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <exclusiveGateway default="default" name="Exclusive Gateway" id="exclusivegateway1"/>

    </sequenceFlow>

      <conditionExpression xsi:type="tFormalExpression">${apidata_method == "GETRECS"}</conditionExpression>

    <sequenceFlow targetRef="task3" sourceRef="exclusivegateway1" name="GET" id="flow14">
      <conditionExpression xsi:type="tFormalExpression">${apidata_method == "GET"}</conditionExpression>
    </sequenceFlow>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="task4" sourceRef="exclusivegateway1" name="PUT" id="flow15">
      <conditionExpression xsi:type="tFormalExpression">${apidata_method == "PUT" || apidata_method == "PATCH"}</conditionExpression>
    </sequenceFlow>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="endevent1" sourceRef="task5" id="flow16"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="endevent1" sourceRef="task3" id="flow17"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="endevent1" sourceRef="task2" id="flow18"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="endevent1" sourceRef="task1" id="flow19"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="endevent1" sourceRef="exclusivegateway1" name="Unsupported" id="default"/>
    <userTask activiti:formKey="poi_default_view" name="Default" id="usertask1"/>
    <userTask activiti:formKey="poi_shareslist_view" name="Shares" id="usertask2"/>
    <userTask activiti:formKey="poi_preview_view" name="Preview" id="usertask3"/>
